{"tid":850320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地產代理襲擊政府監察人員，","createTime":"2018-10-06T11:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T12:12:40.000Z","uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"80eb9977b245d912c7e2b01a2b5cb06f06bdce39","tid":850320,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20181006/photo/bkn-20181006170919647-1006_00842_001_01p.jpg?20181006175051\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20181006%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181006170919647-1006_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20181006175051&h=48a42f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n樓市逆轉，加上地產代理人數創新高，搵食更艱難。面對沉重壓力，代理好易躁火，市傳周六(6日)在旺角始創中心地下、新盤海傲灣的示範單位外，有地產代理與地產代理監管局(EAA)職員發生肢體衝突。期間懷疑有EAA職員倒地，但暫時未知是否受傷。東網就事件向EAA查詢，但暫仍未獲回覆。 <br />\n<br />\n據在場代理表示，有警察到達現場，帶走疑似涉事人士。"},{"pid":"6d218771e26055ecfae18ce2ed255e379d900c39","tid":850320,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:31:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee4474bd5c28094eae597219a31fad16ecc5794","tid":850320,"uid":52358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:33:47.000Z","msg":"又話日日創新高gogogo嘅<br />\n有咩壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6092bc6f7b46c5ee224c67431671a130d9edb50a","tid":850320,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:35:02.000Z","msg":"mk囝嬲嬲豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a8cd5e869035a1177b5969e035928a9b3ddd496","tid":850320,"uid":193026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ee4474bd5c28094eae597219a31fad16ecc5794","tid":850320,"uid":52358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T11:33:47.000Z","msg":"又話日日創新高gogogo嘅<br />\n有咩壓力<img src=\"/assets/fac